---
title: Italian Sausage in Marinara with Parmesan Potato-Cauli Mash
description: This Italian-inspired twist on sausage and mash is sure to be a hit with the whole family! Fragrant Italian pork sausage is cooked in marinara sauce with a soffritto base for maximum flavour. Cheesy potato-cauliflower mash alongside is perfect for those who prefer their veggies hidden!
